 Stakeholder Register Creation 
Create formal stakeholder register
Stakeholder	Role	Interests	Influence Level
Employees	End Users	Easy reporting, quick resolution, transparency	Medium
Security Analysts	System Users	Efficient triage, clear workflows, reduced manual work	High
OC Team	System Users	Real-time monitoring, coordinated response, comprehensive reporting	High
IT Administrators	System Maintainers	System reliability, security, ease of maintenance
	Medium
Management	Sponsors	Risk reduction, compliance, cost-effectiveness	High
Legal & Compliance	Compliance Oversight	Adherence to regulations, proper documentation	Medium
